==French==

===Etymology===
From [[w:Smurfs|The Smurfs]] (originally called ''Les Schtroumpfs'' in French), who used the verb ''schtroumpfer'' to replace other verbs.
===Verb===
'''schtroumpfer'''
# {{frslang}} To [[smurf]]

====Usage note====
This verb can be used to replace any other verb.

